title: The Timmons Incident: Part II of the Timmons Chronicles
description: 'You're paranoid.' are words that Bobby Timmons hears lately. If he is paranoid, there's a good reason for it. He's being watched by his own government! And far do Sarah Brown's powers reach? Into the beyond?The story goes from small town America to the very steps of the Capitol in this explosive sequel to 'Theater Boy.'
author: Michael Fox
